Ares Dynamic Credit Allocation Fund Declares Monthly Distributions of 
      $0.1050 Per Share






July 13, 2017 08:00 AM Eastern Daylight Time



NEW YORK--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Ares Dynamic Credit Allocation Fund, Inc. (the “Fund”) (NYSE:ARDC) 
      announced an increase to its monthly distribution rate from the previous 
      rate of $0.1025 per common share to $0.1050 per common share in order to 
      better align the Funds’ distribution rate with its current and projected 
      level of earnings. The declaration of monthly distributions for the next 
      three months is payable as noted below.
    



           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        

           
        



