         Open   16.45    Day Range   16.43 - 16.50    Volume   44,943    Previous Close   16.44    52Wk Range   14.11 - 16.55    1 Yr Return   26.65%    YTD Return   14.44%    NAV (on 07/25/2017)   17.92000008    Total Assets (m USD) (on 04/30/2015)   316.850    Inception Date   11/28/2012    Premium/Discount   -7.92%    Average 52-Week Premium   -11.82%    Fund Managers   SETH J BRUFSKY / KEITH M ASHTON    Last Dividend (on 08/22/2017)   0.105    Dividend Indicated Gross Yield   7.64%    Expense Ratio   2.39%    3 Mo Return   3.99%    3 Yr Return   6.38%    5 Yr Return   -                     Profile   Ares Dynamic Credit Allocation Fund is a closed-end fund incorporated in the USA. The Fund's objective is to provide an attractive level of total return, primarily through current income and, secondarily, through capital appreciation by investing in a broad, dynamically managed portfolio of (i) senior loans, (ii) high yield bonds, and (iii) investment grade collateralized loan obligations.    Address  Ares Capital Management II LLC2000 Avenue of the Stars12th FloorLos Angeles, CA 90067   Phone  -   Website   www.aresmgmt.com              


